              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37449929/" class="">第290页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/DellaMao/" class=" " title="Della">Della</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37449929">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们的统治者最致命错误，就是过分关注生产成本，而不是交易成本</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-03-26 02:23</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>我们的统治者最致命错误，就是过分关注生产成本，而不是交易成本</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
